quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  10,100,"Ẹ̀mí kan kò lè gbàgbọ́ àfi pẹ̀lú ìyọ̀ǹda Allāhu. Ó sì máa fi ìyà jẹ àwọn tí kò ṣe làákàyè.{1}.",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah at-Taobah; 9:13.]
  10,101,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ wòye sí n̄ǹkan tí ń bẹ nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀. Àwọn āyah àti ìkìlọ̀ kò sì níí rọ ìjọ aláìgbàgbọ́ lọ́rọ̀.”"
  10,102,"Nítorí náà, ṣé wọ́n tún ń retí (n̄ǹkan mìíràn) ni bí kò ṣe (ìparun) irú ti ọjọ́ àwọn tó ré kọjá lọ ṣíwájú wọn. Sọ pé: “Ẹ máa retí nígbà náà. Dájúdájú èmi náà wà pẹ̀lú yín nínú àwọn olùretí.”"
  11,67,"Ohùn igbe líle gbá àwọn tó ṣàbòsí mú. Wọ́n sì dà lulẹ̀, tí wọ́n ti dòkú sínú ìlú wọn."
  11,68,"Àfi bí ẹni pé wọn kò gbénú ìlú náà rí.{1} Gbọ́, dájúdájú ìran Thamūd ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú Olúwa wọn. Kíyè sí i, kí ìjìnnà sí ìkẹ́ máa jẹ́ ti ìjọ Thamūd..",footnotes:1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, wọ́n ṣẹ̀mí fún ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ ọdún, àmọ́ wọ́n parẹ́ láààrin ìṣẹ́jú kan.]
  11,69,"Dájúdájú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Wa ti mú ìró ìdùnnú wá bá (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm. Wọ́n sọ pé: “Àlàáfíà (fún ọ).” Ó sọ pé: “Àlàáfíà (fún yín).” Kò sì pẹ́ rárá tó fi gbé ọmọ màálù àyangbẹ wá."
  12,28,"Nígbà tí (ọkọ) rí ẹ̀wù rẹ̀ tí wọ́n ti fà á ya lẹ́yìn, ó sọ pé: “Dájúdájú nínú ète ẹ̀yin obìnrin ni (èyí). Dájúdájú ète yín tóbi."
  12,29,"Yūsuf, ṣẹ́rí kúrò níbi èyí. Kí ìwọ (obìnrin yìí) sì tọrọ àforíjìn fún ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ rẹ. Dájúdájú ìwọ wà lára àwọn aláṣìṣe.”"
  12,30,"Àwọn obìnrin kan nínú ìlú sọ pé: “Ayaba ń jírẹ̀ẹ́bẹ̀ fún eré ìfẹ́ lọ́dọ̀ ọmọ ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ̀; ìfẹ́ kúkú ti kó sí i lọ́kàn. Dájúdájú àwa ń rí òun pé ó wà nínú àṣìṣe pọ́nńbélé.”"